snippet.title: Cursorblade - Demo Trailer
snippet.description: Cursorblade is a bullet hell where you play as a cursor that fights your way through waves of enemies. Combine weapons and items to be more powerful with your own unique builds. Slash, dodge, upgrade and repeat!
